# Attestack

This repository records AI-assisted work with [Attestack](https://kiket-dev.github.io/attestack/).

## Session

Before substantive changes, ensure a session is open:

```bash
attestack start "short task title"
```

## Recording evidence

Prefer Attestack MCP tools:

- `attestack_status`, `attestack_note`, `attestack_agent_tool_call`, `attestack_agent_decision`, `attestack_snapshot`

Run verification commands through Attestack:

```bash
attestack run -- npm test
```

Use hashes instead of raw prompts when recording AI content.

## Finish

```bash
attestack stop
attestack bundle create
```
